00:22:40.660 --> 00:22:42.070
&gt;&gt; Lincoln Peirce: Yeah,
that was the dream.

00:22:42.070 --> 00:22:43.670
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Very much so.

00:22:43.670 --> 00:22:44.970
Yeah.

00:22:44.970 --> 00:22:46.270
&gt;&gt; Lincoln Peirce: And there he is.

00:22:46.270 --> 00:22:47.570
