00:23:22.600 --> 00:23:24.310
This is tremendous.

00:23:24.310 --> 00:23:26.280
And at the time, this was
before the Wimpy Kid --

00:23:26.280 --> 00:23:30.760
this was his first book, and it
was just starting to get traction.

00:23:30.760 --> 00:23:35.290
So I tracked him down, I said,
Jeff, you know, congratulations.

00:23:35.290 --> 00:23:42.050
We got back in touch, and he,
long story short, he helped me.

00:23:42.050 --> 00:23:47.130
