years remained a big Nate fan.

00:23:47.130 --> 00:23:50.300
And he said you should
have a book deal.

00:23:50.300 --> 00:23:51.600
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Wow.

00:23:51.600 --> 00:23:52.900
Wow.

00:23:52.900 --> 00:23:54.200
&gt;&gt; Lincoln Peirce: Yeah.

00:23:54.200 --> 00:23:55.500
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: And he was
growing his at this point

00:23:55.500 --> 00:23:56.800 position:56%
to a half billion dollar enterprise.

