I write the books for kids.

00:26:01.360 --> 00:26:05.970
You know, ages basically
7 to 12 or so.

00:26:05.970 --> 00:26:08.800
And so it's a different kind
of writing, but I ended up --

00:26:08.800 --> 00:26:10.410 position:56%
