Eight is enough, as it were.

00:26:18.130 --> 00:26:19.430
&gt;&gt; Lincoln Peirce: Yeah.

00:26:19.430 --> 00:26:20.730
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Yeah.

00:26:20.730 --> 00:26:22.030
