books either.

00:26:44.950 --> 00:26:47.660
So that's why I like the
name hybrid for them,

00:26:47.660 --> 00:26:49.630
because they combine
the text and the comics.

00:26:49.630 --> 00:26:52.280
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Yeah, it did
