own balance, and also, some of them,

00:27:01.450 --> 00:27:03.750
I know, aim at like 6th
grade boys and girls.

00:27:03.750 --> 00:27:06.750
They're trying to figure out
what is their sweet spot.

00:27:06.750 --> 00:27:11.390
Did you kind of play with your
own balance levels, if you will?

00:27:11.390 --> 00:27:16.990
&gt;&gt; Lincoln Peirce: I just think,
like I call myself a rhythm writer.

00:27:16.990 --> 00:27:21.710
So when I write, I just hear
the dialogue in my head.

00:27:21.710 --> 00:27:26.960 position:56%
I hear what the kids are saying,
and just the rhythm has to be right.

00:27:26.960 --> 00:27:35.130 position:56%
And it just suggests to me like
well, this I can just write in text.

00:27:35.130 --> 00:27:38.910
