00:27:48.100 --> 00:27:52.560
with kids is, you know,
show not tell.

00:27:52.560 --> 00:27:53.860
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Yeah, yeah.

00:27:53.860 --> 00:27:56.660
&gt;&gt; Lincoln Peirce: And they love
-- it's like, if you're going to --

